Name: CHATEAU GISCOURS
Description: There is lovely creamy blackcurrant and strawberry fruit here, with a persistence that is ever so attractive. This is really excellent. It exhibits a dense purple colour in addition to an excellent bouquet of black fruits, smoke, earth, and minerals, supple tannin, an excellent texture and a long, fine finish.
